_sText:
This map was a test of a Stargate Ring transporters, but i decided to make a simple map Knife Arena/Funny stuff like mini game.

Features:
- Ring Transporters
- Time bomb ( can send throught Ring transporters :D )
- 60+ spawns ( but map is not bigger )
- Full of explosive barrells, CT's can throw it to terrorists heads :D
